    Page: 86
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Death
---
At the time of death, the mind forgets the existing body and enters into
another body. Whether you will it or not, what is designed to happen will
certainly happen as ordained by God. Hence, it is advisable to leave all
sorrows to God and live in peace.
